query:
insert into ap_users
        (
            ap_id,
            username,
            inbox_url,
            public_key,
            private_key,
            last_refreshed_at,
            display_name,
            bio,
            -- insert id, but don't update it below
            id
        )
        values ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
        on conflict(ap_id) do update set
            ap_id = $1,
            username = $2,
            inbox_url = $3,
            public_key = $4,
            private_key = $5,
            last_refreshed_at = $6,
            display_name = $7,
            bio = $8
        returning *
